# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-105">Политика защиты от потери данных (DLP) в Центре соответствия требованиям включает множество типов конфиденциальной информации, готовых к использованию в политиках защиты от потери данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-106">В этой статье перечислены все эти типы конфиденциальной информации и показано, каким именно образом политика защиты от потери данных выявляет каждый тип.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-107">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-108">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-109">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-110">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из этих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-110">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-111">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-112">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-113">Номер маршрутки ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-113">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-114">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-114">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-115">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-115">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-116">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-116">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-117">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-117">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-118">четыре цифры, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-118">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-119">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-119">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-120">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-120">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-121">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-121">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-122">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-122">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-123">Неформатированные: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-123">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-124">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-124">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-125">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-125">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-126">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-126">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-127">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-127">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-128">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-128">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-129">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-129">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-130">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-130">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-131">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-131">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-141">bankrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-141">bankrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-142">bankroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-142">bankroutingnumber</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-146">routing transit number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-146">routing transit number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-147">routing #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-147">routing#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-148">RTN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-148">RTN</span></span>


## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-149">Номер удостоверения личности для Аргентины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-149">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-150">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-150">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-151">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-151">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-152">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-152">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-153">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-153">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-154">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-154">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-155">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-155">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-156">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-156">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-157">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-157">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-158">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-158">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-159">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-159">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-160">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-160">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-161">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-161">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-162">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-162">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-163">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-163">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-164">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-164">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-176">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-176">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-177">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-178">от шести до десяти цифр с номером филиала банковского состояния или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-178">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-179">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-180">Номер учетной записи — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-180">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-181">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-181">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-182">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-182">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-183">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-183">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-184">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-184">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-185">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-186">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-186">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-187">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-188">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-188">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-189">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-189">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-190">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-190">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-191">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-191">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-192">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-192">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-193">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-193">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-194">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-194">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-195">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-195">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-196">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-196">Keyword_australia_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-197">swift bank code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-197">swift bank code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-198">correspondent bank</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-198">correspondent bank</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-199">base currency</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-199">base currency</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-210">Номер компании для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-210">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-211">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-211">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-212">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-212">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-213">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-213">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-214">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-214">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-215">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-215">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-216">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-216">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-217">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-218">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-218">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-219">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-220">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-220">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-221">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-221">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-222">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-222">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-223">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-223">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-224">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-224">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-225">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-225">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-226">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-226">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-227">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-227">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-228">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-229">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-229">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-230">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-231">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-231">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-232">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-232">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-233">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-233">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-234">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-234">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-235">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-235">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-238">australia business no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-238">australia business no</span></span>

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-245">Номер компании для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-245">Australia company number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-246">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-246">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-247">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-247">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-248">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-248">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-249">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-249">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-250">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-250">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-251">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-251">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-252">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-252">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-253">девять цифр с делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-253">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-254">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-254">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-255">девять цифр с делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-255">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-256">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-256">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-257">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-257">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-258">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-258">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-259">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-259">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-260">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-260">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-261">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-262">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-262">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-263">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-263">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-264">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-264">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-265">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-265">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-266">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-266">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-267">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-267">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-268">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-268">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-278">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-278">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-279">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-279">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-280">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-280">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-281">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-281">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-282">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-282">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-283">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-283">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-284">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-284">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-285">пять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-285">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-286">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-286">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-287">от одной до двух необязательных букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-287">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-288">от четырех до девяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-288">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-289">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-289">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-290">девять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-290">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-291">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-291">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-292">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-292">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-293">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-293">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-294">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-294">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-295">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-295">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-296">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-296">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-297">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-297">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-298">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-298">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-299">Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-299">Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-300">international driving permits</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-300">international driving permits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-301">australian automobile association</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-301">australian automobile association</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-302">international driving permit</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-302">international driving permit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-303">DriverLicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-303">DriverLicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-304">DriverLicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-304">DriverLicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-305">Driver Lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-305">Driver Lic</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-397">Номер медицинской учетной записи для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-397">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-398">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-398">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-399">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-399">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-400">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-400">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-401">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-401">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-402">первая цифра находится в диапазоне от 2 до 6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-402">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-403">девятая цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-403">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-404">десятая цифра — это цифра проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-404">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-405">одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — это отдельный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-405">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-406">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-406">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-407">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-407">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-408">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-408">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-409">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-409">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-410">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-410">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-411">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-411">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-412">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-412">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-413">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-413">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-414">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-414">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-415">bank account details</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-415">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-416">medicare payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-416">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-417">mortgage account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-417">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-418">bank payments</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-418">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-419">information branch</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-419">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-420">credit card loan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-420">credit card loan</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-421">department of human services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-421">department of human services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-422">local service</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-422">local service</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-423">1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-423">medicare</span></span>

   
## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-424">Номер паспорта гражданина Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-424">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-425">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-425">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-426">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-426">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-427">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-427">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-428">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-428">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-429">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-429">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-430">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-430">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-431">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-431">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-432">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-432">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-433">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-433">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-434">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-434">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-468">Номер налогового файла для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-468">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-469">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-470">от восьми до девяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-470">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-471">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-472">От восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представлены пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-472">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-473">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-473">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-474">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-474">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-475">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-475">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-476">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-476">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-477">две-три цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-477">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-478">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-478">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-479">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-479">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-480">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-480">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-481">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-481">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-482">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-482">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-483">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-483">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-484">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-484">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-496">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-496">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-497">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-497">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-498">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-498">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-499">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-499">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-500">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-500">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-501">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-501">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-502">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-502">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-503">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-503">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-504">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-504">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-505">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-505">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-506">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-506">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-633">Удостоверение личности для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-633">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-634">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-634">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-635">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-635">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-636">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-636">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-637">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-637">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-638">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-638">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-639">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-639">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-640">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-640">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-641">24-значное сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-641">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-642">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-642">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-643">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-643">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="92c93-644">22 буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты или знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-644">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-645">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты, знаки плюс или знаки равного знака</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-645">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-646">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-646">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-647">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-647">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-648">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-648">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-649">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-649">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-650">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-650">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-651">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-651">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-652">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-652">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-653">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-653">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-654">identity number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-654">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-655">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-655">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-656">personalausweis repubich österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-656">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-657">Номер паспорта гражданина Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-657">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-658">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-659">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательное пространство и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-659">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-660">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-661">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-661">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-662">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-662">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-663">одно пространство (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-663">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-664">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-664">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-665">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-665">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-666">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-666">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-667">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-667">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-668">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-668">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-669">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-669">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-670">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-670">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-671">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-671">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-672">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-672">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-673">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-673">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-674">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-674">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-695">Номер социального обеспечения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-695">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-696">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-696">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-697">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-697">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-698">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-698">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-699">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-699">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-700">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-700">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-701">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-701">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-702">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-702">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-703">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-703">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-704">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-704">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-705">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-705">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-706">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-706">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-707">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-707">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-708">находится ключевое слово  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` из.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-708">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-709">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-709">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-710">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-710">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-736">Идентификационный номер налога для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-736">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-737">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-737">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-738">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-738">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-739">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-739">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-740">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-740">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-741">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-741">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-742">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-742">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-743">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-743">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-744">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-744">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-745">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-745">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-746">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-746">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-747">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-747">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-748">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-748">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-749">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-749">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-750">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-750">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-751">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-751">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-752">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-752">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-753">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-753">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-776">Налог на добавленную стоимость для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-776">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-777">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-777">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-778">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-778">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-779">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-779">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-780">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-780">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-781">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-781">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-782">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-782">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-783">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-783">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-784">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-784">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-785">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-785">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-786">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-786">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-787">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-787">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-788">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-788">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-789">Дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-789">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-790">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-790">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-791">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-791">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-792">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-792">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-793">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-793">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-794">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-794">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-795">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-795">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-796">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-796">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-797">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-797">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-798">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-798">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-799">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-799">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-800">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-800">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-801">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-801">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-802">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-802">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-803">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-803">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-804">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-804">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-810">vat no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-810">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-811">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-811">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-812">номер налога на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-812">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-813">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-813">austrian vat</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-819">идентификационный номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-819">vat identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-820">atu number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-820">atu number</span></span>
