## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1514">Номер водительского удостоверения для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1514">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1515">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1515">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1516">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1516">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1517">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1517">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1518">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1518">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1519">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1519">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1520">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1520">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1521">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1521">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1522">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1522">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1523">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1523">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1524">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1524">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1652">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1652">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1653">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1653">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1654">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1654">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1655">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1655">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1656">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1656">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1657">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1657">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1658">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1659">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1659">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1660">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1661">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1661">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1662">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1662">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1663">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1663">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1664">одна цифра, соответствующая полу: четная цифра для самца и нечетная цифра для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1664">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1665">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1665">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1666">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1666">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1667">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1667">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1668">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1668">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1669">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1669">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1670">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1670">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1671">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1671">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1672">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1672">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1673">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1673">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1718">Номер паспорта гражданина Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1718">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1719">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1719">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1720">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1720">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1721">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1721">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1722">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1722">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1723">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1723">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1724">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1724">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1725">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1725">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1726">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1726">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1727">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1727">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1728">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1728">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1729">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1729">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1730">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1730">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1731">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1731">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1732">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1732">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1752">Номер банковского счета для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1752">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1753">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1753">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1754">семь или двенадцать цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1754">seven or twelve digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1755">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1755">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1756">Номер банковского счета для Канады — семь или двенадцать цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1756">A Canada Bank Account Number is seven or twelve digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1757">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1757">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1758">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1758">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1759">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1759">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1760">три цифры ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1760">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1761">ноль "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1761">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1762">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1762">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1763">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1763">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1764">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1764">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1765">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1765">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1766">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1766">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1767">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1767">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1768">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1768">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1769">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1769">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1770">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1770">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1771">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1771">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1772">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1772">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1796">Номер водительского удостоверения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1796">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1797">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1797">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1798">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1798">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1799">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1799">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1800">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1800">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1801">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1802">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1802">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1803">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1804">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1804">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1805">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1805">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1806">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1806">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1807">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1807">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1943">Номер службы здравоохранения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1943">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1944">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1944">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1945">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1945">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1946">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1946">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1947">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1947">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1948">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1948">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1949">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1949">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1950">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1950">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1951">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1951">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1952">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1952">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1953">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1953">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1956">personal health number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1956">personal health number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1958">health services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1958">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1959">speciality services</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1959">speciality services</span></span>

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1965">Номер паспорта гражданина Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1965">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1966">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1966">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1967">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1967">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1968">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1968">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1969">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1969">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1970">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1970">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1971">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1971">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1972">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1972">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-1973">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1973">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1974">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1974">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1975">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1975">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1976">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1976">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-1977">Keyword_canada_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1977">Keyword_canada_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-1978">canadian citizenship</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-1978">canadian citizenship</span></span>

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2005">Персональный идентификационный номер медицинского удостоверения для Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2005">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2006">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2006">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2007">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2007">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2008">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2008">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2009">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2009">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2010">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2010">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2011">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2011">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2012">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2012">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2013">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2013">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2014">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2014">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2015">Найдено по крайней мере два ключевых Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2015">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2048">Номер социального страхования для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2048">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2049">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2049">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2050">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2050">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2051">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2051">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2052">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2052">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2053">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2053">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2054">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2054">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2055">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2055">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2056">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2056">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2057">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2057">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2058">Неформатированные: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2058">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2059">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2059">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2060">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2060">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2061">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2061">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2062">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2062">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2063">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2063">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2064">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2064">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2065">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2065">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2066">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2066">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2067">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2067">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2068">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2068">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2069">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2069">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2070">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2070">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2071">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2071">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2072">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2072">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2097">Номер удостоверения личности для Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2097">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2098">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2098">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2099">от семи до восьми цифр, а также делегировка контрольной цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2099">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2100">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2100">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2101">семь–восемь цифр, а также делегаторы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2101">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2102">одна–две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2102">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2103">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2103">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2104">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2104">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2105">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2105">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2106">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2106">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2107">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2107">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2108">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2108">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2109">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2109">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2110">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2110">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2111">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2111">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2112">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2112">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2113">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2113">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2114">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2114">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2115">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2115">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2116">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2116">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2117">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2117">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2118">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2118">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2155">Номер удостоверения личности резидента Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2155">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2156">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2156">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2157">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2157">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2158">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2158">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2159">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2159">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2160">шесть цифр, которые являются кодом адреса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2160">six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2161">восемь цифр в формате YYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2161">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2162">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2162">three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2163">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2163">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2164">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2164">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2165">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2165">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2166">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2166">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2167">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2167">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2168">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2168">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2169">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2169">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2170">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2170">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2171">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2171">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2172">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2172">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2173">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2173">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2174">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2174">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2175">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2175">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2176">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2176">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2177">КНР</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2177">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2178">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2178">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2179">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2179">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2180">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2180">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2181">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2181">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2182">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2182">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2183">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2183">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2184">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2184">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2185">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2185">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2186">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2186">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2187">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2187">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2188">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (ddd), и которые должны пройти проверку Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2188">14 to 16 digits which can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and which must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2189">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2189">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2190">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон, который определяет карты всех основных мировых стандартов, включая Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карты Diners Club.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2190">Very complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2191">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2191">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2192">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2192">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2193">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2193">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2194">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2194">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2195">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2195">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2196">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2196">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2197">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2197">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2198">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2198">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2199">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2199">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2200">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2200">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2201">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2201">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2202">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2202">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2203">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2203">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2464">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2464">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2465">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2465">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2466">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2466">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2467">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2467">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2468">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2468">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2469">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2469">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2470">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2470">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2471">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2471">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2472">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2472">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2473">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2473">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2598">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации для национального идентификационных номеров ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2598">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2599">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2599">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2600">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2600">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2601">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2601">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2602">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2602">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2603">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2603">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2604">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2604">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2605">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2605">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2606">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2606">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2607">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2607">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2608">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2608">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2639">Номер паспорта гражданина Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2639">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2640">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2640">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2641">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2641">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2642">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2642">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2643">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2643">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2644">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2644">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2645">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2645">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2646">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2646">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2647">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2647">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2648">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2648">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2649">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2649">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2650">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2650">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2651">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2651">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2652">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2652">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2653">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2653">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2666">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2666">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2671">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер (OIB) для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2671">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2672">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2672">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2673">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2673">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2674">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2674">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2675">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2675">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2676">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2676">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2677">окончательная цифра — это провероальная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2677">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2678">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2678">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2679">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2679">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2680">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2680">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2681">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2681">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2682">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2682">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2683">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2683">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2684">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2684">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2685">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2685">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2686">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2686">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2687">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2687">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2688">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2688">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_croatia_oib_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2689">Keyword_croatia_oib_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2689">Keyword_croatia_oib_number</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2718">Номер водительского удостоверения для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2718">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2719">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2719">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2720">12 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2720">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2721">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2721">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2722">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2722">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2723">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2723">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2724">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2724">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2725">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2725">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2726">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2726">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2727">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2727">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2728">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2728">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2853">Удостоверение личности для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2853">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2854">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2854">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2855">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2855">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2856">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2856">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2857">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2857">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2858">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2858">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2859">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2859">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2860">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2860">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2861">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2861">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2862">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2862">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2863">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2863">ten digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2864">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2864">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2865">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2865">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2866">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2866">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2867">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2867">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2868">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2868">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2869">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2869">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2870">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2870">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2871">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2871">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2872">id card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2872">id card number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2874">kim karti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2874">kimlik karti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2875">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2875">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2876">личный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2876">personal id number</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2878">Номер паспорта гражданина Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2878">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2879">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2879">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2880">одна буква, за которой следуют 6–8 цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2880">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2881">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2881">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2882">одна буква, за которой следуют от шести до восьми цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2882">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2883">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2884">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2884">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-2885">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2886">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2886">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2887">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2887">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2888">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2888">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2889">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД/ММ/YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2889">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-2890">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2890">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2891">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2891">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-2892">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-2892">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
