-   <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6233">уникальный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6233">unique id</span></span>  

   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6234">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6234">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6235">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6235">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6236">сочетание 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6236">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6237">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6237">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6238">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6238">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6239">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6239">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6240">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6240">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6241">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6241">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6242">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6242">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6243">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6243">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6244">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6244">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6245">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6245">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6246">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6246">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6247">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6247">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6248">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6248">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6249">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6249">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6250">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6250">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6251">numero di patente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6251">numero di patente</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6252">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6252">patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6253">patente guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6253">patente guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6254">patenti di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6254">patenti di guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6255">patenti guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6255">patenti guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6256">Финансовый код Для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6256">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6257">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6257">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6258">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6258">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6259">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6259">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6260">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6260">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6261">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6261">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6262">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6262">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6263">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6263">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6264">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6264">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6265">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6265">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6266">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6266">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6267">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6267">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6268">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6268">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6269">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6269">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6270">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A в E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6270">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6271">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6271">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6272">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, относя к замурованию человека (коды на территории страны используются для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6272">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6273">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6273">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6274">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6275">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6275">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6276">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6277">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6277">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6278">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6278">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6279">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6279">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6280">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6280">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6281">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6281">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6316">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6316">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6317">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6317">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6318">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6318">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6319">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6319">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6320">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6320">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6321">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6321">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6322">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6322">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6323">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6323">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6324">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6324">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6325">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6325">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6326">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6326">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6327">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6327">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6328">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6328">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6329">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6329">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6330">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6330">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6331">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6331">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6332">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6332">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6356">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6356">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6357">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6357">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6358">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6358">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6359">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6359">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6360">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6360">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6361">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6361">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6362">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6362">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6363">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6363">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6364">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6364">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6365">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6365">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6366">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными делетерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6366">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6367">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6367">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6368">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6368">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6369">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6369">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6370">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6370">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6371">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6371">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6372">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6372">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6373">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6373">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6374">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6374">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6375">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6375">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6376">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6376">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6377">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6377">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6378">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6378">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6386">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6386">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6387">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6387">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6388">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6388">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6389">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6389">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6390">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6390">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6391">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6391">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6392">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6392">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6393">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6393">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6394">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6394">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6395">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6395">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6396">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6397">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6397">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6398">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6399">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6399">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6400">Функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6400">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6401">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6401">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6402">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6402">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6403">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6403">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6404">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6404">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6405">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6405">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6406">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6406">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6407">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6407">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6456">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6456">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6458">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6458">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6459">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6459">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6460">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6460">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6461">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6461">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6462">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6462">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6463">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6463">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6464">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6464">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6502">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6502">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6503">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6503">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6504">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6504">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6505">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6505">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6506">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6506">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6507">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6507">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6508">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6508">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6509">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6509">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6510">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6510">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6511">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6511">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6512">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6512">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6513">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6513">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6514">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6514">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6515">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6515">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6516">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6516">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6517">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6517">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6518">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6518">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6519">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6519">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6520">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6520">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6521">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6521">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6522">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6522">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6541">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6541">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6542">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6542">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6543">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6543">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6544">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6544">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6545">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6545">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6546">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6546">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6547">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6547">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6548">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6548">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6549">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6549">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6550">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6550">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6551">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6551">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6552">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6552">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6553">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6553">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6554">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6554">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6555">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6555">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6556">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6556">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6557">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 65 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6557">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6558">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6558">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6563">個人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6563">個人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6564">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6564">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6565">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6565">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6566">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6566">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6567">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6567">個人番号カード</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6569">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6569">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6570">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6570">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6571">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6571">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6572">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6572">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6573">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6573">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6574">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6574">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6575">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6575">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6576">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6576">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6577">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6577">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6578">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6578">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6579">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6579">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6580">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6580">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6581">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6581">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6598">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6598">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6599">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6599">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6600">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6600">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6601">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6601">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6602">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6602">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6603">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6603">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6604">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6604">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6605">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6605">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6606">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6606">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6607">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6607">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6608">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6608">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6609">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6609">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6610">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6610">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6611">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6611">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6612">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6612">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6614">Номер карты для проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6614">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6615">Карточка", "Без карты проживания"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6615">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6616">Карточка для проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6616">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6617">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6617">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6618">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6618">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6619">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6619">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6620">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6620">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6621">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6621">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6622">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6622">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6623">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6623">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6624">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6624">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6625">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6625">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6626">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6626">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6627">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6627">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6628">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6628">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6629">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6629">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6630">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6630">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6631">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6631">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6632">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6632">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6643">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6643">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6645">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6645">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6647">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6647">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6648">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6648">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6649">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6649">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6650">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6650">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6651">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6651">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6653">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6653">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6655">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6655">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6656">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6656">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6657">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6657">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6658">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6658">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6659">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6659">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6660">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6660">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6681">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6681">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6682">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6683">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6683">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6684">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6685">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6685">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6686">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6686">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6687">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6687">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6688">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6689">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6689">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6690">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6691">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6691">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6692">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6692">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6693">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6693">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6818">Персональный код для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6818">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6819">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6820">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6820">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6821">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6822">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6822">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6823">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6823">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6824">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6824">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6825">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6825">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6826">одна цифра, соответствующая годовщине рождения ("0" для 19-го, "1" для 20-го и "2" для 21-го)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6826">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6827">четыре цифры, генерируемые случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6827">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6828">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6828">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6829">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6829">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6830">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6830">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6831">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6831">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6832">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6832">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6833">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6833">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6834">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6834">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6835">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6835">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6836">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6836">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6837">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6837">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6838">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6838">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6839">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6839">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6902">Номер паспорта гражданина Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6902">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6903">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6903">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6904">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6904">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6905">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6905">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6906">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6906">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6907">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6907">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6908">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6908">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6909">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6909">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6910">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6910">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6911">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6911">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6912">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6912">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6913">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6913">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6914">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6914">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6915">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6915">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6916">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6916">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6917">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6917">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6918">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6918">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6941">Номер водительского удостоверения для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6941">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6942">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6942">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6943">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6943">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6944">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6944">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6945">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6945">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6946">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6946">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6947">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6947">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-6948">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6948">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-6949">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6949">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6950">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6950">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-6951">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-6951">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7076">Персональный код Для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7076">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7077">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7077">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7078">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7078">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7079">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7079">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7080">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7080">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7081">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7081">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7082">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7082">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7083">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7083">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7084">11 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7084">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7085">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7085">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7086">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7086">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7087">одна цифра (1–6), соответствующая полу и возрасту человека при рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7087">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7088">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7088">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7089">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7089">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7090">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7090">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7091">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7091">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7092">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7092">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7093">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7093">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7094">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7094">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7095">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7095">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7096">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7096">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7097">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7097">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7098">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7098">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7133">Номер паспорта гражданина Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7133">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7134">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7134">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7135">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7135">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7136">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7136">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7137">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7137">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7138">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7138">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7139">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7139">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-7140">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7140">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7141">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7141">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7142">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7142">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7143">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7143">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7144">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7144">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-7145">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7145">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7146">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7146">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-7147">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-7147">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
