## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10127">SQL Server подключения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10127">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10128">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10128">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10129">Строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10129">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10130">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10130">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10131">строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10131">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10132">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10132">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10133">строка "Password" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует строчная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10133">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" is not preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10134">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10134">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10135">любой символ, который не является знаком доллара ($), символом процента (%), больше символа (>), в символе (@), кавычках ("), точка с зазнаковкой (;), левая скобка ([) или левая скобка ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10135">any character that is not a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10136">любое сочетание 7–128 символов, которые не являются пустяковой (;) косой черты (/) или кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10136">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10137">точка с зачетом (;) или кавычка (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10137">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10138">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10138">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10139">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10139">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10140">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10140">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10141">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10141">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10142">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10142">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10143">Ключевое слово из CEP_GlobalFilter **не** найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10143">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter is **not** found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10144">Регулярное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10144">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10145">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10145">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10173">Номер водительского удостоверения для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10173">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10174">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10175">десять цифр, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10175">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10176">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10177">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10177">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10178">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10178">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10179">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10179">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10180">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10180">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10181">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10181">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10182">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10182">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10183">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10183">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10184">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10184">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10185">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10185">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10186">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10186">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10319">Национальный ИД Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10319">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10320">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10320">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10321">10 или 12 цифр и необязательный седиметр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10321">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10322">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10322">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10323">10 или 12 цифр и необязательный делегатор:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10323">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10324">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10324">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10325">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10325">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10326">либо "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10326">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10327">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10327">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10328">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10328">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10329">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10329">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10330">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10330">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10331">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10331">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10332">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10332">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10333">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10333">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10334">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10334">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10335">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10335">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10336">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10336">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10337">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10337">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10356">Номер паспорта гражданина Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10356">Sweden passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10357">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10357">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10358">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10358">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10359">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10359">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10360">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10360">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10361">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10361">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10362">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10362">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10363">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10363">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10364">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10364">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10365">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10365">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10366">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10366">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10367">Верно одно из следующих:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10367">one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10368">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10368">a keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10369">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_sweden_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10369">a keyword from Keyword_sweden_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
<Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10400">Идентификационный номер налога для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10400">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10401">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10401">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10402">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10402">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10403">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10403">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10404">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10404">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10405">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10405">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10406">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10406">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10407">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10407">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10408">десять цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10408">ten digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10409">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10409">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10410">десять цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10410">ten digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10411">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10411">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10412">знак "плюс" или "минус"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10412">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10413">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10413">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10414">для номеров, выдавшихся до 1990 г., седьмая и восьмая цифры определяют округ рождения или инородных людей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10414">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10415">цифра в девятом положении указывает пол по нечетным для самцов или даже для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10415">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10416">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10416">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10417">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10417">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10418">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10418">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10419">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10419">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10420">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10420">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10421">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10421">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10422">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10422">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10423">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10423">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10424">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10424">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10450">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10450">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10451">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10451">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10452">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют от 5 до 31 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10452">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10453">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10453">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10454">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют 5–31 буква или цифры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10454">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10455">4-буква банковского кода (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10455">four-letter bank code (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10456">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10456">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10457">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10457">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10458">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10458">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10459">от одной до трех букв или цифр (оставшаяся часть BBAN);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10459">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10460">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10460">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10461">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10461">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10462">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10462">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10463">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10463">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10464">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10464">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10465">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10465">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10466">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10466">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10502">Номер АЧЧ для швейцарии SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10502">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10503">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10503">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10504">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10504">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10505">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10505">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10506">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10506">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10507">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10507">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10508">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10508">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10509">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10509">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10510">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10510">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10511">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10511">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10512">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10512">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10513">три цифры — 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10513">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10514">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10514">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10515">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10515">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10516">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10516">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10517">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10517">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10518">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10518">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10519">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10519">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10520">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10520">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10521">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10521">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10522">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10522">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10523">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10523">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10524">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10524">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10525">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10525">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10526">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10526">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10527">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10527">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10548">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10548">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10549">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10549">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10550">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10550">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10551">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10551">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10552">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10552">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10553">одна буква (на английском языке без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10553">one letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10554">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10554">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10555">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10555">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10556">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10556">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10557">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10557">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10558">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10558">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10559">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10559">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10560">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10560">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10561">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10561">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10562">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10562">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10563">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10563">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10564">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10564">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10565">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10565">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10582">Номер паспорта гражданина Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10582">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10583">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10583">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10584">биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10584">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10585">Номер не биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10585">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10586">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10586">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10587">биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10587">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10588">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10588">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10589">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10589">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10590">не биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10590">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10591">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10591">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10592">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10592">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10593">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10593">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10594">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10594">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10595">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10595">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10596">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10596">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10597">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10597">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10600">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10600">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10601">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10601">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10602">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10602">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10603">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10603">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10604">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10604">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10605">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10605">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10606">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10606">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10607">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10607">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10608">Номер сертификата резидента Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10608">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10609">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10610">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10610">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10611">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10611">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10612">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10612">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10613">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10613">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10614">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10614">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10615">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10615">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10616">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10616">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10617">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10617">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10618">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10618">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10619">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10619">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10620">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10620">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10628">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10628">ARC</span></span>

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10634">Идентификационный код для тайских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10634">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10635">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10635">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10636">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10636">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10637">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10637">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10638">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10638">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10639">первая цифра не нуль или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10639">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10640">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10640">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10641">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10641">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10642">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10642">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10643">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10643">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10644">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10644">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10645">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10645">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10646">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10646">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10647">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10647">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10648">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10648">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10649">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10649">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10651">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10651">ID Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10653">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10653">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10654">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10654">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10655">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10655">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10656">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10656">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10657">Идентификационный номер гражданина Турецкий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10657">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10658">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10659">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10659">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10660">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10661">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10661">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10662">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10662">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10663">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10663">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10664">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10664">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10665">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10665">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10666">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10666">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10667">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10667">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10668">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10668">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10669">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10669">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10670">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10670">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10671">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10671">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10672">TC Kim kim</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10672">TC Kimlik No</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10675">Vatanda vat vatk no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10675">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10676">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10676">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10677">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10677">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10678">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10678">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10679">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10679">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10680">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10680">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10681">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10681">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10682">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10682">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10683">пять букв (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" на месте буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10683">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10684">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10684">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10685">пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения (7-й знак приращен на 50, если драйвер — женщина, то есть от 51 до 62 вместо 01–12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10685">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10686">две буквы (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10686">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10687">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10687">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10688">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10689">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10689">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10690">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10691">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10691">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10692">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10692">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10693">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10693">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10694">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10694">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10704">10</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10704">motorcycles</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10709">driving licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10709">driving licences</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10710">driving licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10710">driving licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10711">dual control car</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10711">dual control car</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10712">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10712">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10713">roll number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10713">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10714">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10714">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10715">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1–4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10715">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10716">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10716">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10717">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют 1–4 числа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10717">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10718">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10718">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10719">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10719">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10720">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10720">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10721">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10721">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10722">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10722">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10723">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10723">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10724">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10724">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10725">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10725">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10727">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10727">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10728">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10728">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10729">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10729">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10730">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10730">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10731">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10731">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10732">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10732">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10733">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10733">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10734">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10734">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10735">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10735">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10736">три или десять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10736">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10737">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10737">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10738">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10738">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10739">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10739">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10740">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10740">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10741">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10741">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10742">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10742">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10743">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10743">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10744">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10744">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10745">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10745">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10746">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10746">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10747">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10747">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10748">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10748">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10749">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10749">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10750">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10750">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10751">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10751">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10752">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10752">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10761">patient number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10761">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10762">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10762">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10763">GP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10763">GP</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10764">DOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10764">DOB</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10765">D.O.B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10765">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10766">Date of Birth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10766">Date of Birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10767">Birth Date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10767">Birth Date</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10768">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10768">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10769">national insurance number (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10769">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10770">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации "National Identificaiton Number" в ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10770">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10771">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10771">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10772">семь или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10772">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10773">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10773">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10774">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10774">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10775">две буквы (допустимые niNOs используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который проверяется этим шаблоном; без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10775">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10776">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10776">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10777">либо "A", "B", "C", либо "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10777">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10778">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10778">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10779">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10779">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10780">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10780">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10781">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10781">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10782">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10782">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10783">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10783">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10784">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10784">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10785">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10785">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10786">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10786">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10787">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10787">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10788">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10788">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10789">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10789">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10790">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10790">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10791">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10791">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10792">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10792">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10793">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10793">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10794">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10794">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10795">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10795">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10817">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10817">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10818">Уникальный справочный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10818">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10819">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10819">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10820">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10820">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10821">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10821">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10822">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10822">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10823">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10823">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10824">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10824">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10825">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10825">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10826">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10826">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10827">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10827">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10828">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10828">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10829">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10829">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10830">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10830">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10831">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10831">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10832">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10832">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10833">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10833">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10834">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10834">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10854">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10854">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10855">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10855">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10856">6–17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10856">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10857">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10857">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10858">6–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10858">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10859">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10859">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10860">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10860">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="92c93-10861">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10861">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="92c93-10862">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10862">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10863">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10863">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="92c93-10864">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="92c93-10864">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
